LineQuestionComposite is a CompositeForm
    is primary
    title is "SourcingEventLineQuestion"
    context form is QuestionContext
        background is theme color
    Question is a Panel
        form is Questions
    YesNoAnswer is a Panel
        visible when (YesNoQuestionWithWeighting)
        list is SourcingEventLineQuestionAllocation set.QuestionYesNoAnswers
    YesNoTextAnswer is a Panel
        visible when (YesNoTextQuestionWithWeighting)
        list is SourcingEventLineQuestionAllocation set.QuestionYesNoTextAnswers
    ListAnswers is a Panel
        visible when (ListQuestion)
        list is SourcingEventLineQuestionValue set.SELQuestionValue
    AllocationListAnswer is a Panel
        title is "WeightingAllocations"
        visible when (ListQuestionWithWeighting)
        list is SourcingEventLineQuestionAllocation set.QuestionListAnswers
